<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6688] Traits cannot modify their internal variables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6688</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;trait Level {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; maxLevel
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; currentLevel = 0
    
    void foo() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;( currentLevel &amp;lt; maxLevel ) {
            currentLevel += 1
        }
    }
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Leveller &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; Level {
    Leveller() {
        maxLevel = 3
    }
}

def v = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Leveller()
v.foo()
v.foo()
v.foo()
v.foo()
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; v.currentLevel == 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fails with &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Assertion failed: 

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; v.currentLevel == 3
       | |            |
       | 0            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
       Leveller@1f757867
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But if you change the trait to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;trait Level {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; maxLevel
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; currentLevel = 0
    
    void foo() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;( Level__currentLevel &amp;lt; maxLevel ) {
            Level__currentLevel += 1
        }
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It works...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m guessing this is a bug, as the given example (&lt;a href=&quot;http://beta.groovy-lang.org/docs/groovy-2.3.0-beta-1/html/documentation/core-traits.html#_private_fields&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://beta.groovy-lang.org/docs/groovy-2.3.0-beta-1/html/documentation/core-traits.html#_private_fields&lt;/a&gt;) of:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;trait Counter {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; count = 0                   
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; count() { ++count }                 
}
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; Counter {}             
def f = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo()
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; f.count() == 1  
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;doesn&apos;t work if you add:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; f.count() == 2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to the bottom&lt;/p&gt;</description>
